<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-15-1160 </DOCNO><TEXT>This and succeeding letters discuss the James and Kilbey (1977 and 1978)model for the initiation of u.v. mutagenesis in Saccharomyces cerevisiaeand its application to include a number of chemical mutagens. The Baranowskaet al (1987) results indicating the role of DNA replication, the differingmechanisms in Escherichia coli, are all discussed.</TEXT></DOC>